name: So I Became a Witch and Started Doing Daily Quests
summary: "Hello, esteemed Miss Janna Roland. How do you feel about having received the title of [Most Charming Witch], awarded by Wizard Weekly, for three consecutive years?""To be honest, rather than that title, I prefer the way other wizards refer to me.""You don't mean: Master of Life, Keeper of Summoning Laws, Spirit Realm’s Dearest, Guardian of the Four Seasons, Soul Singer...?""None of those.""I prefer to be called — the Erudite Wizard."
author: Marctempest
